included.summary:
My academic training is in human-computer interaction, communication, and social psychology. I utilize a mixed-method approach to generate ideas, understand people, and evaluate products and opportunities. Methods in my toolkit include survey methodology and related statistical analysis, interviewing and other qualitative approaches, and server data analysis and visualization. 

At Facebook, I work closely with design and engineering on the News Feed product.
